1
00:00:22,389 --> 00:00:27,292
纽泽西州纽沃市 九月

2
00:00:49,384 --> 00:00:54,014
汤尼 别忘了告诉路易叔叔…我把红酒和巴马干酪留在冰箱里
Don't forget to tell Uncle Louie I left the red wine and Parmesan in the fridge.

3
00:00:54,097 --> 00:00:55,724
拜拜 好
I love you. Bye -bye.

4
00:00:55,807 --> 00:00:57,768
-拜拜 裘蒂 -寄照片来喔
-'Bye, Judy. -Send me a picture.

5
00:00:57,893 --> 00:00:59,936
我很快回来 别担心
I'll be back soon. Don't worry about it.

6
00:01:00,103 --> 00:01:02,773
-小心点 -拜
-Be careful, now. -Bye.

7
00:01:04,191 --> 00:01:07,027
-保重啦 -拜!
-Take it easy, now. -'Bye.

8
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,556
加州 我们来啦
"California, here we come"

9
00:01:37,099 --> 00:01:39,434
来 丹尼尔 怎么啦? 不喜欢我唱歌?
What's wrong? Don't you like my singing?

10
00:01:39,559 --> 00:01:40,852
妈 我不喜欢那首歌
I don't like the song.

11
00:01:40,977 --> 00:01:43,980
你会喜欢加州的 你早上起床
You're going to love California. You get up in the morning...

12
00:01:44,106 --> 00:01:45,982
滚出床外 咚! 就掉进游泳池里了
... roll out of bed, plop, in the pool.

13
00:01:46,191 --> 00:01:47,192
是哦
Yeah, sure.

14
00:01:47,442 --> 00:01:51,321
你看着吧 我们要搬进的可不是破旧小屋喔
You'll see. This isn't exactly a dump we're moving to.

15
00:02:53,139 --> 00:02:58,042
峡谷口汽车旅馆

16
00:03:00,515 --> 00:03:04,978
推呀 丹尼尔 用力推! 用尽全力推! 加油!
Push, Daniel. Give it all you've got, kid. Push!

17
00:03:05,937 --> 00:03:09,274
好了 发动了 快快 跳进来!
Okay, we've got it. Come on. Get in, hurry up.

18
00:03:12,152 --> 00:03:15,072
你又办到啦 好极了!
We did it again. Way to go!

19
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:44,893
醒来
Daniel, wake up.

20
00:03:44,976 --> 00:03:49,439
看看右舷方向 总算来到乐园了!
Look off the starboard bow. Paradise at last.

21
00:03:50,649 --> 00:03:52,192
我们到了
We made it.

22
00:03:52,818 --> 00:03:54,611
来吧
Come on.

23
00:03:54,694 --> 00:03:55,946
就是这里
This is it.

24
00:03:56,780 --> 00:03:59,282
这里是终点站
This is the end of the line.

25
00:04:00,158 --> 00:04:01,618
还用你说
You're telling me.

26
00:04:02,536 --> 00:04:04,955
来吧 开始行动
Come on. All hands on deck.

27
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:10,419
我们得在车子下沉前 把行李拿光
We've got to get this thing unloaded before it sinks.

28
00:04:12,337 --> 00:04:16,049
看看那些棕榈树! 哇塞! 你知道这代表什么吗?
Look at those palm trees! Damn, do you know what that means?

29
00:04:16,258 --> 00:04:18,677
小心会有椰子掉下来
Yeah, watch out for falling coconuts.

30
00:04:18,927 --> 00:04:22,848
-聪明鬼 再没有纽沃的冬天啦! -妈 我喜欢冬天
-Wise guy. No more Newark winters. -I like winters.

31
00:04:22,973 --> 00:04:25,892
你喜欢喉咙痛? 冰冷的脚趾头?
Oh, you like sore throats? You like frozen toes?

32
00:04:26,268 --> 00:04:27,644
我不喜欢烟雾
I don't like smog.

33
00:04:27,894 --> 00:04:31,148
-我说过这里有游泳池了没? -妈 你说过100次了
-Did I tell you about the pool here? -About 100 times.

34
00:04:31,273 --> 00:04:33,567
好吧 再说第101次
Okay, so make it 101.

35
00:04:33,692 --> 00:04:38,321
睁开眼睛 我亲爱的儿子 这是伊甸园哪!
Open your eyes, my darling son. This is the Garden of Eden.

36
00:04:38,405 --> 00:04:42,033
来 我们住20号公寓 知道吧?
Come on. Listen, we're in apartment 20, okay?

37
00:04:42,242 --> 00:04:44,035
要上楼
One flight up.

38
00:05:03,263 --> 00:05:05,307
-你还好吧? -我没事 别担心
-Are you okay? -Don't worry about it.

39
00:05:05,557 --> 00:05:07,100
-我扶你 -谢啦
-Let me help you up. -Thanks.

40
00:05:07,309 --> 00:05:09,269
你没事? 我不该那么做的 别担心
I shouldn't have done that. It was stupid.

41
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:11,730
你一定是刚搬进20号公寓的人
You must be the new people in 20, right?

42
00:05:11,855 --> 00:05:12,898
我想是吧
Yeah, I guess so.

43
00:05:13,106 --> 00:05:15,484
-佛莱迪菲南德斯 17号公寓 -丹尼尔拉罗素
-Freddy Fernandez, apartment 17. -Daniel LaRusso.

44
00:05:15,692 --> 00:05:16,985
你好 我帮你拿
How you doing? Let me help.

45
00:05:17,110 --> 00:05:20,697
-不必 很重的 -我来拿 没关系
-No, it's fine. It's heavy, man. -I got it.

46
00:05:21,239 --> 00:05:23,116
-你从哪里来? -纽泽西州
-Where are you from? -New Jersey.

47
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,743
你来这里做什么?
What are you doing out here?

48
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:28,163
我妈在这里的公司找到工作
My mom got a job with some company out here. Rocket Computers.

49
00:05:28,288 --> 00:05:29,998
火箭 电脑 未来航班 我不知道
Flight of the Future. I don't know.

50
00:05:30,123 --> 00:05:32,959
-没听过 -很有发展的
-I never heard of it. -It's up and coming.

51
00:05:33,835 --> 00:05:38,298
-这就是你们这里唯一的游泳池? -对 就是那个 嘿 你那是空手道吗?
-Is this the only pool you've got? -That's it. What was that, karate?

52
00:05:39,424 --> 00:05:41,760
-是的 -你练了很久?
-Yeah. -Have you been doing it long?

53
00:05:41,885 --> 00:05:44,262
-一阵子 -用过吗?
-Yeah, a while. -Did you ever use it?

54
00:05:44,388 --> 00:05:47,224
-几次 -用来打架一定不错吧?
-A couple of times. -I bet you could kick some ass.

55
00:05:47,391 --> 00:05:50,310
我有空也想学学 你可以教我
I'd like to learn that. Maybe you could teach me.

56
00:05:50,435 --> 00:05:52,479
-当然 随时都可以 -太好了
-Sure. That's cool. Anytime. -Great.

57
00:05:52,604 --> 00:05:55,690
这地方很烂 你该回到纽泽西去的
This place is a dump. You should go back to New Jersey.

58
00:05:56,858 --> 00:05:58,485
你怎知道我从泽西来?
How did you know where I was from?

59
00:05:58,610 --> 00:06:01,530
因为我是从纽泽西来 我可以看得出来
'Cause I'm from New Jersey. I got a nose for my own.

60
00:06:01,655 --> 00:06:04,241
-从哪里? -帕斯潘尼
-Well what part? -Parsippany.

61
00:06:04,408 --> 00:06:07,411
-当初真不该离开 -我有个路易叔叔就是帕斯潘尼人
-I never should've left. -My Uncle Louie's from Parsippany.

62
00:06:07,619 --> 00:06:09,162
-路易凡提尼? -路易拉罗素
-Louie Martini? -Louie LaRusso.

63
00:06:09,287 --> 00:06:11,873
路易拉罗素 不认识
Louie LaRusso? Don't know him.

64
00:06:12,457 --> 00:06:14,501
嗨 小狗
Hey, pup.

65
00:06:14,710 --> 00:06:16,753
你怎么样? 很渴吗?
How you doing? You thirsty?

66
00:06:17,504 --> 00:06:19,214
-她是疯子 -什么?
-She's crazy. -What?

67
00:06:19,339 --> 00:06:22,008
-她脑筋不太正常 -她很好啊
-She's not playing with a full deck. -She's nice.

68
00:06:22,134 --> 00:06:25,137
-你明天要做什么? -我不知道 没事吧
-What are you doing tomorrow? -I don't know. I guess nothing.

69
00:06:25,303 --> 00:06:28,306
我们有个海滩派对 有点像告别夏天的 你想来吗?
We're having a beach party. Want to come?

70
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:31,476
-当然 那太棒了 -好 我明天来接你
-Sure, that's cool. -I'll come get you in the morning.

71
00:06:32,018 --> 00:06:33,895
好 这里就是20号公寓
Here's apartment 20.

72
00:06:34,062 --> 00:06:35,856
-这里? -我放在这里罗?
-Is it? -Should I leave this here?

73
00:06:35,981 --> 00:06:38,817
-好 谢谢你帮忙 -没问题
-Yeah, thanks for the help. -No problem.

74
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:42,779
-很高兴认识你 -我也是 -保重 明天见 -好
-Nice meeting you. -Sure -Take care. See you tomorrow morning. -All right

75
00:06:44,906 --> 00:06:48,744
别跟我提游泳池 我明天一大早就打电话去问
Don't say anything about the pool. I'll call first thing in the morning.

76
00:06:48,910 --> 00:06:51,663
你跟那个老女人说我们从哪来了?
Did you tell that old lady where we were from?

77
00:06:51,747 --> 00:06:53,874
对啊 她会让你想起泰西婶婶吧?
Yes. Didn't she remind you of Aunt Tessy?

78
00:06:54,833 --> 00:06:58,628
-泰西婶婶? 比较像路易叔叔 -我真觉得我们在这里会过得很快乐
-More like Uncle Louie. -I really think we're going to do good here.

79
00:06:58,754 --> 00:07:01,506
告诉你 丹尼尔 我对这里的感觉很好
I have a very positive feeling. I'm telling you, Daniel.

80
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:04,593
我知道一定会顺利的 水龙头坏了
I just know it's going to work. The faucet's broken.

81
00:07:04,676 --> 00:07:08,722
仲介小姐说有个修理工住在这里 你能不能去找他?
The real estate lady said there's a fix -it guy. See if you can find him.

82
00:07:10,474 --> 00:07:11,558
那是干嘛的?
What's that for?

83
00:07:12,184 --> 00:07:13,977
-这个? 要给路易叔叔的小狗 -它很可爱
-Uncle Louie's dog. -He's cute.

84
00:07:14,061 --> 00:07:16,980
-妈 有人邀请我明天去一个派对 好呀 我就说吧?
-I got invited to a party tomorrow. -Great. You see?

85
00:07:17,230 --> 00:07:21,109
-我知道 但你要我帮你整理东西 -我可不记得说过这件事
-But you wanted me to help you unpack. -I don't remember saying that.

86
00:07:22,235 --> 00:07:25,322
好极了 我一定把你跟其他人弄混了
I must have had you mixed up with somebody else.

87
00:07:25,447 --> 00:07:26,656
妈 谢啦
Thanks, Ma.

88
00:07:30,619 --> 00:07:32,996
你知道修理工人在哪吗?
Could you tell me where the maintenance guy is?

89
00:07:33,288 --> 00:07:34,748
嗨 小子 给你喝
Hey, pup.

90
00:07:34,873 --> 00:07:38,585
你走进那边 左转 不要走远…
You go in through there, turn left, not too far...

91
00:07:38,835 --> 00:07:41,755
然后右转 进去 你会看到他在左边
... then right, go inside, and you'll find him on the left.

92
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,423
所以我先右转再左转
So I go right then left?

93
00:07:43,548 --> 00:07:46,968
不对 左 然后右 然后左边的里面
No, left then right, then inside on the left.

94
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,656
哈罗?
Hello?

95
00:08:14,704 --> 00:08:16,415
你是修理工吗?
Are you the maintenance man?

96
00:08:18,333 --> 00:08:20,544
我们刚搬进20号公寓
We're the new people in apartment 20.

97
00:08:22,713 --> 00:08:25,298
我们的水龙头漏水了
The faucet's really leaking there.

98
00:08:31,471 --> 00:08:33,098
你能来修吗?
Could you come fix it?

99
00:08:37,185 --> 00:08:38,812
我能去告诉我妈何时吗?
Can I tell my mom when?

100
00:08:39,521 --> 00:08:40,731
什么何时?
When what?

101
00:08:42,691 --> 00:08:44,484
你何时来修水龙头
When you're going to fix the faucet.

102
00:08:44,651 --> 00:08:45,694
以后
After.

103
00:08:46,570 --> 00:08:48,029
在什么以后?
After what?

104
00:08:48,155 --> 00:08:49,781
以后!
After after!

105
00:09:40,582 --> 00:09:43,835
请把球还我好吗? 谢谢
Could we have the ball, please?

106
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,462
他很不错
Pretty good.

107
00:09:45,712 --> 00:09:47,089
卖弄
Show -off.

108
00:09:50,717 --> 00:09:53,970
拜 嗨 等等!
Sorry. Hey, wait up.

109
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:59,476
-穿蓝衣的金发女孩是谁? --山庄的
-Who's that blonde in the blue? -The hills.

110
00:09:59,935 --> 00:10:02,604
-什么是山庄的? -有钱人
-What's the hills? -Rich.

111
00:10:20,453 --> 00:10:22,318
-喂 丹尼尔 -什么?
-hey, Daniel -What?

112
00:10:22,374 --> 00:10:25,210
-我觉得那个金发女孩在看你 -是哦
-I think the blonde is looking at you. -Yeah, right.

113
00:10:25,293 --> 00:10:29,423
-我说真的啦 我觉得她喜欢你喔 -这也不能怪她 对吧 佛莱迪?
-I think she has the hots for you. -Who could blame her?

114
00:10:29,715 --> 00:10:32,217
-那你为什么不去搭讪? -不要 我在吃东西
-Why don't you make a move? -No, I'm eating, man.

115
00:10:32,342 --> 00:10:35,095
-你怎么还能想到吃? 去搭讪啦 -我饿呀
-How can you think about eating? -I'm hungry.

116
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:39,599
-或许他老家那边的人都没胆子 -我有胆子
-Maybe they ain't got no moves in Jersey. -I got moves where I come from.

117
00:10:39,808 --> 00:10:43,395
-我们那边的人比这里更有胆 -是吗?
-We've got more moves back there than here, I'll tell you that much. -Yeah?

118
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:46,148
做来看看
Let's see 'em.

119
00:10:48,108 --> 00:10:50,068
来吧 伙计 去追她
Come on, buddy. Go get her.

120
00:10:50,235 --> 00:10:52,446
-好 我去了 -去追她
-I'm going. -Go

121
00:10:53,653 --> 00:10:55,177
我在走了啦
I'm going.

122
00:10:55,282 --> 00:10:57,784
-你掉了什么吗? -希望我们没吵到你
-Lose something? -I hope we're not bothering you.

123
00:10:57,909 --> 00:10:59,953
你怎么玩球的?
Hey, how do you juggle?

124
00:11:00,036 --> 00:11:05,000
很简单 我先从膝盖开始 你先踢一下
It's pretty easy. You start on the knee. You just go one.

125
00:11:05,167 --> 00:11:08,253
一次一下 一 然后试踢两下 一 二
One at a time. Then you try two. One, two.

126
00:11:09,379 --> 00:11:12,883
你试试 三 四 试试看 把脚抬高 一 对啦!
And then three and four. Try it. Just bring your leg up. Good!

127
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:24,519
-看哪! 真了不起! -啤酒时间到! 谁要烫手的?
-That was awesome! -Brew time. Who's for a warm one?

128
00:11:24,644 --> 00:11:25,812
不 谢了
No, I pass.

129
00:11:27,064 --> 00:11:29,316
你开什么玩笑? 你是最糟的
Who are you kidding? You're the ace degenerate.

130
00:11:29,649 --> 00:11:34,529
不 最烂的! 明早8点 我就升级了 我还有一年的时间可以努力
Ex -degenerate. Tomorrow I'm a senior. I've got one year to make it all work.

131
00:11:34,613 --> 00:11:38,408
-我就是要这样 要成功 一切 怎样? -好耶 老兄
-And that's what I'm gonna do. Make it work, all of it.-That right.

132
00:11:38,533 --> 00:11:42,454
强尼 你一定是领导流行的人 看起来大家都有新鲜事做
You must be a trendsetter, Johnny. Everyone's doing something new.

133
00:11:42,579 --> 00:11:44,122
往右边看一下
Take a right. Check it out.

134
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:49,669
-强尼 算了吧 已经是历史了 -谁说的?
-Forget it, man. It's ancient history. -Who told you, man?

135
00:11:50,754 --> 00:11:53,048
-我以为他们分手了 -她分了 他可没有
-I thought they broke up. -She did, he didn't.

136
00:11:55,258 --> 00:11:56,635
来 再试一次
Come on, try it.

137
00:11:56,802 --> 00:11:58,345
看好喔
Watch this.

138
00:11:59,763 --> 00:12:01,556
我去拣 马上回来
I'll get it. I'll be right back.

139
00:12:18,907 --> 00:12:21,910
-艾莉 我有话跟你说 -别烦我
-Ali, I want to talk to you. -Leave me alone.

140
00:12:22,244 --> 00:12:24,538
我们该谈的都谈过了 对吧? 我不想谈
We've been over all this. I don't want to talk.

141
00:12:24,913 --> 00:12:27,249
哦 我要跟你说话 不行吗?
I want to talk to you, all right?

142
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:32,045
-你有什么问题? -你为什么不离开?
-What is your problem? -Just get out of here.

143
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:35,924
-好 这样就解决一切问题了 -收音机还我
-That won't solve anything. -Give me my radio.

144
00:12:36,091 --> 00:12:37,634
还我收音机!
I said, give me my radio.

145
00:12:37,926 --> 00:12:40,679
-那你答应跟我说话? -好 先还我收音机
-You promise you'll talk to me? -Yes, give me my radio.

146
00:12:45,934 --> 00:12:48,437
-你摔坏我的收音机了? -对
-You just broke my radio! -Yeah.

147
00:12:48,895 --> 00:12:50,605
别碰 呆子 你聋子吗?
Don't touch it, punk.

148
00:12:53,817 --> 00:12:56,653
-喂 怎么回事 -你要?
-What's going on? -You want it?

149
00:12:56,669 --> 00:12:58,474
-给你! -好耶!
-Get it! -All right!

150
00:13:01,847 --> 00:13:03,405
打呀 丹尼尔

151
00:13:05,537 --> 00:13:07,330
强尼 住手!
Johnny, stop it.

152
00:13:11,501 --> 00:13:14,171
-住手! -我什么也没做
-Stop it. -I didn't do anything.

153
00:13:20,010 --> 00:13:21,803
你是个大人物?
You're a big man now, huh?

154
00:13:22,637 --> 00:13:25,474
喂 是你开头的 我只是想跟你说话而已
You started this. I just wanted to talk.

155
00:13:26,141 --> 00:13:29,770
-那就放开他 我们去说话 -这谎话我好像听过吧?
-Leave him alone and we'll talk. -Where did I hear that before?

156
00:13:31,188 --> 00:13:33,690
你呢 大英雄? 够了吗?
How about you, hero? Had enough?

157
00:13:36,109 --> 00:13:39,196
-好 现在我们平手了 -别心软
