你怎知道我从那里来?
How did you know I was from there?

242
00:21:04,641 --> 00:21:06,977
-我问过了 -真的?
-I asked. -Oh, really?

243
00:21:07,894 --> 00:21:10,647
-你跟谁坐? -可以的话 跟你坐
-Are you sitting with anybody? -With you, if it's okay.

244
00:21:10,731 --> 00:21:13,275
-好呀 你要牛奶吗? -好 谢谢
-Sounds great to me. Want some milk? -Thanks.

245
