00:21:21,074 --> 00:21:24,578
-空手道王吗? -他是我前任男朋友
-Yeah, King Karate? -He's my ex -boyfriend.

248
00:21:25,078 --> 00:21:26,872
能知道真好 什么?
That's good to know. What?

249
00:21:27,914 --> 00:21:29,458
没错 我知道…
Yeah, you're right. I know.

