00:26:56,118 --> 00:26:59,746
我只想回家! 为什么我们不能回家!
I hate it, I want to go home! Why can't we just go back home?

317
00:27:00,789 --> 00:27:02,332
-听我说 -什么?
-Listen to me. -What?

318
00:27:02,416 --> 00:27:05,168
除非你告诉我怎么回事 否则我帮不上忙
I cannot help you unless you tell me what's wrong.

319
00:27:05,293 --> 00:27:06,753
我非学空手道不可 就这样!
I've got to take karate.

320
00:27:06,878 --> 00:27:10,590
-你学过呀 -不 不是在YMCA 要在好学校
-You took karate. -Not at the Y, at a good school.

321
00:27:10,799 --> 00:27:14,302
-打架并不能解决问题 -棕榈树也不能
-Fighting doesn't solve anything. -Neither does palm trees.

322
00:27:14,386 --> 00:27:15,929
这样说不公平
That's not fair.

323
00:27:16,430 --> 00:27:20,559
没事先问过我就跑来这里 难道就很公平?
It wasn't fair coming out here without asking me.

324
00:27:23,270 --> 00:27:24,396
你说得对
You're right.

325
00:27:25,772 --> 00:27:27,065
我该问问你的
I should've asked.

326
00:27:27,190 --> 00:27:30,944
我只想回家 如此而已 我不懂这里的规则
I just want to go home. I don't understand the rules here.

327
00:27:31,069 --> 00:27:34,156
我们来想办法看看能不能 一起找出这里的规则 好不好?
Let's see if we can figure out the rules together.

328
00:27:34,281 --> 00:27:37,451
-你的脚踏车怎么办? -搭公车安全多了
-What about your bike? -It's safer taking the bus.

329
00:27:37,576 --> 00:27:41,246
为什么我们不能回家 把这地方忘掉?
Why can't we just go home and forget this place?

330
00:28:03,393 --> 00:28:06,146
-我会告诉你他说的每句话 -最好这样
-I'll tell you everything he said. -You'd better.

331
00:28:19,201 --> 00:28:20,327
嗨 你好吗?
How are you?

332
00:28:20,452 --> 00:28:24,414
-你的额头怎么啦? -糟透了 长了个超大的青春痘
-What happened to your forehead? -It's terrible. A gigantic runaway zit.

333
00:28:24,539 --> 00:28:26,333
真恶心 -
That's gross.

334
00:28:27,084 --> 00:28:30,754
丹尼尔 这是苏珊 到底发生了什么事?
Daniel, this is Susan. What really happened?

335
00:28:30,879 --> 00:28:32,839
我骑车摔了 但我没事
I got in a bike accident.

336
00:28:33,882 --> 00:28:36,802
你骑什么车? 本田? 铃木?
What kind of bike do you have? A Honda? Suzuki?

337
00:28:38,261 --> 00:28:40,138
不 是宫城涡轮
It's a Miyagi Turbo.

338
00:28:40,263 --> 00:28:42,557
-真的? -真的?
-Yeah? -Oh, really?

339
00:28:42,682 --> 00:28:45,769
-我们要去打电动玩具 你要一起来吗? -当然 好极了
-We're going to the arcade. Want to come? -Sounds great.

340
00:28:45,852 --> 00:28:48,522
你一定要看看这个新游戏 我弄给你看
There's this new game I want to show you.

341
00:28:52,401 --> 00:28:57,030
我突然想起来了 我忘了一个东西 我晚点再去找你们
I forgot something. I'll catch up with you guys in a minute.

342
00:28:57,114 --> 00:28:59,866
-你不需要逃走 -我没有逃走
-Don't run away. -I'm not running away from anything.

343
00:29:00,158 --> 00:29:04,287
-总该有个对策 -你用你的方式去应付 我用我的方式 我要走了
-We've got to deal with this. -I'll deal with it my own way.

344
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:07,290
-丹尼尔… -别管我!
-Daniel... -Get off my case!

345
00:29:44,703 --> 00:29:47,956
你修了我的脚踏车?
Did you fix my bike?

346
00:29:48,373 --> 00:29:50,584
-谢谢 --不客气
-Thank you. -You're welcome.

347
00:29:50,709 --> 00:29:52,753
我真的很感激
I really appreciate that.

348
00:29:54,963 --> 00:29:56,506
那些是真的树吗?
Are those real trees?

349
00:29:57,507 --> 00:29:59,968
你想看就进来
You like see, come inside.

350
00:30:00,802 --> 00:30:01,887
谢谢
Thanks.

351
00:30:10,103 --> 00:30:11,897
怎么长得这么小?
How did they get so small?

352
00:30:12,022 --> 00:30:13,565
我修剪的
I train.

353
00:30:13,815 --> 00:30:16,193
这里剪一点 那里修一下
Clip here, tie there.

354
00:30:17,319 --> 00:30:19,196
你在哪学的? 日本吗?
Did you learn this in Japan?

355
00:30:19,362 --> 00:30:20,572
冲绳
Okinawa.

356
00:30:20,697 --> 00:30:21,865
那是哪里?
Where's that?

357
00:30:22,574 --> 00:30:23,825
我的国家
My country.

358
00:30:25,494 --> 00:30:26,745
中国 这里
China here.

359
00:30:27,162 --> 00:30:28,622
日本 这里
Japan here.

360
00:30:28,997 --> 00:30:30,791
冲绳 这里
Okinawa here.

361
00:30:32,834 --> 00:30:34,461
你去学校学的吗?
Did you go to school for this?

362
00:30:34,544 --> 00:30:35,796
父亲教的
Father teach.

363
00:30:36,546 --> 00:30:38,006
他是园丁?
Was he a gardener?

364
00:30:38,632 --> 00:30:39,800
渔夫
Fisherman.

365
00:30:39,966 --> 00:30:41,176
渔夫?
A fisherman.

366
00:30:42,427 --> 00:30:44,221
真漂亮
These are really beautiful.

367
00:30:45,055 --> 00:30:46,515
来 你试试
Come, you try.

368
00:30:46,681 --> 00:30:48,558
我不知道该怎么做
I don't know how to do this stuff.

369
00:30:48,683 --> 00:30:51,436
-坐下不 -我会弄砸的 我不想把它弄砸
-Sit down. -I may mess it up or something.

370
00:30:52,646 --> 00:30:54,022
闭上眼睛
Close eyes.

371
00:30:55,982 --> 00:30:56,983
信任
Trust.

372
00:31:01,029 --> 00:31:02,280
专心
Concentrate.

373
00:31:04,241 --> 00:31:06,701
只想树
Think only tree.

374
00:31:08,537 --> 00:31:12,374
想像一幅图画 连一针一叶都不忽略
Make a perfect picture down to last pine needle.

375
00:31:13,834 --> 00:31:18,130
澄清你的心灵 除了树之外什么都不想
Wipe your mind clean. Everything but the tree.

376
00:31:19,798 --> 00:31:22,801
世界上什么都没有
Nothing exists in whole world...

377
00:31:23,135 --> 00:31:25,262
只有树
... only tree.

378
00:31:27,556 --> 00:31:28,682
好了吗?
You got it?

379
00:31:30,058 --> 00:31:31,601
睁开眼睛
Open eyes.

380
00:31:33,019 --> 00:31:34,479
记得那图?
Remember picture?

381
00:31:35,689 --> 00:31:36,773
记得
Yeah.

382
00:31:37,733 --> 00:31:39,276
照那图来剪
Make like picture.

383
00:31:48,869 --> 00:31:51,163
只要信任那图
Just trust the picture.

384
00:31:52,205 --> 00:31:54,541
但我怎么知道我的图是对的?
How do I know my picture's the right one?

385
00:31:54,666 --> 00:31:58,503
如果来自你内心 一定是对的
If come from inside you, always the right one.

386
00:32:33,121 --> 00:32:34,164
嗨
Hi.

387
00:32:34,956 --> 00:32:36,500
嘿 妈 进来吧
Hi, Ma, come on in.

388
00:32:38,043 --> 00:32:41,296
-你修好脚踏车了 -不 宫城先生修好的
-You fixed your bike. -Mr. Miyagi fixed it.

389
00:32:42,672 --> 00:32:44,132
哇 太棒了 谢谢你
Great, thank you.

390
00:32:45,175 --> 00:32:47,427
-我们该给你多少钱? -不用钱
-How much do we owe you? -No, please.

391
00:32:47,677 --> 00:32:48,845
我的荣幸
My pleasure.

392
00:32:49,221 --> 00:32:50,680
那真好
That's very nice.

393
00:32:53,141 --> 00:32:54,393
哈罗 小冠军
Hi, champ.

394
00:32:54,935 --> 00:32:55,936
嗨
Hey.

395
00:32:57,104 --> 00:33:01,149
-你在做什么? -我在修剪我的小树
-What are you doing? -I'm trimming my baby tree.

396
00:33:01,691 --> 00:33:03,068
盆栽树
Bonsai tree.

397
00:33:03,693 --> 00:33:04,820
盆栽树
Bonsai tree.

398
00:33:05,195 --> 00:33:06,196
盆栽
Bonsai.

399
00:33:06,863 --> 00:33:07,864
盆栽
Bonsai.

400
00:33:08,907 --> 00:33:09,991
好漂亮
They're beautiful.

401
00:33:10,117 --> 00:33:12,953
宫城先生在冲绳学的 他从那里来
Mr. Miyagi learned it in Okinawa. That's where he's from.

402
00:33:13,161 --> 00:33:14,162
真的?
Really?

403
00:33:14,287 --> 00:33:15,831
好精致
They're so delicate.

404
00:33:20,961 --> 00:33:22,170
给我?
For me?

405
00:33:22,713 --> 00:33:24,423
不 我不能收
No, I couldn't.

406
00:33:24,506 --> 00:33:26,717
请收下 别让我难过
Please, hurt feelings.

407
00:33:28,135 --> 00:33:30,011
你真好 谢谢
That's very nice, thank you.

408
00:33:30,595 --> 00:33:32,931
-不客气 -我知道该放哪里
-Welcome. -I know just where it will go.

409
00:33:33,932 --> 00:33:35,559
走吧 不早了
Come on, it's getting late.

410
00:33:35,726 --> 00:33:38,895
-好 我在过半小时就上去 -不 我们现在就走 明天要上学
-I'll be up in a half hour. -No, now. School tomorrow.

411
00:33:40,063 --> 00:33:42,816
-真是谢谢你 -不客气
-Thank you for everything. -You're welcome.

412
00:33:44,818 --> 00:33:46,528
别忘了树
Don't forget tree.

413
00:33:47,988 --> 00:33:49,197
要练习
Must practice.

414
00:33:50,198 --> 00:33:51,283
谢谢
Thank you.

415
00:33:51,408 --> 00:33:53,535
-莎哟娜拉 -莎哟娜拉
 -Sayonara. -Sayonara.

416
00:33:54,411 --> 00:33:56,872
-晚安 -再次谢谢你 再见
-Goodnight. -Thanks again. See you.

417
00:34:00,542 --> 00:34:03,545
他把最棒的给我了 他真的好特别
Ma, he gave you the nicest one. This guy is something else.

418
00:34:03,795 --> 00:34:06,798
你看到他把我脚踏车修好了 这人真棒
You saw what he did to my bike. This guy is great.

419
00:34:37,454 --> 00:34:41,583
-丹尼尔桑 万圣节快乐 喜欢吗? -嗯 不错
-Happy Halloween. You like? -Yeah, that's nice.

420
00:34:41,792 --> 00:34:44,544
学校今天都好? 很多事发生
Passed school today. Lots happening.

421
00:34:46,505 --> 00:34:48,715
怎么回事? 你不去?
What's the matter? You're not going?

422
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:49,841
没
No.

423
00:34:50,467 --> 00:34:51,468
为什么?
How come?

424
00:34:52,135 --> 00:34:54,262
我不太喜欢跳舞
I'm not into dancing that much.

425
00:34:55,764 --> 00:34:57,474
反正我也不想跳
I don't feel like it, anyway.

426
00:34:59,559 --> 00:35:02,229
丹尼尔桑 你太孤僻了 不好
You're too much by self. Not good.

427
00:35:03,105 --> 00:35:04,481
我没有孤僻
I'm not by myself.

428
00:35:05,315 --> 00:35:06,566
我跟你在一起
I'm with you.

429
00:35:07,526 --> 00:35:12,239
要做蜂蜜 小蜜蜂需要新鲜花朵 不是老梅子
To make honey, young bee need young flower, not old prune.

430
00:35:13,156 --> 00:35:15,200
反正我也没有服装
I don't have a costume, anyway.

431
00:35:15,951 --> 00:35:17,494
有服装
If have costume...

432
00:35:18,078 --> 00:35:19,162
你就去?
... you go?

433
00:35:19,830 --> 00:35:21,957
如果我能变隐形人的话 或许吧
If I went as the Invisible Man.

434
00:35:22,708 --> 00:35:24,418
隐形人"?
Invisible Man?

435
00:35:25,877 --> 00:35:28,088
你知道 就是没人能看见我
You know, so no one would see me.

436
00:35:44,855 --> 00:35:46,231
嗨 那是丹尼尔
There's Daniel.

437
00:35:46,398 --> 00:35:48,108
-哪里? -那个淋浴室
-Where? -In the shower.

438
00:35:48,191 --> 00:35:50,652
-你怎么知道? -我就是知道
-How do you know? -I just know.

439
00:35:50,777 --> 00:35:51,945
借我?
May I?

440
00:35:53,071 --> 00:35:56,908
-不晓得她喜欢他哪一点 -她一定有问题
-I don't know what she sees in him. -She must be into fungus.

441
00:36:01,663 --> 00:36:04,332
救我! 我的花需要水!
Help me, my flower needs water.

442
00:36:05,792 --> 00:36:08,462
你来对地方了 陌生人
You've come to the right place, stranger.

443
00:36:09,629 --> 00:36:13,383
-我从没有在浴室里跳过舞 -我一个朋友做的 好有趣
-I've never danced in a shower. -A friend of mine made this for me.

444
00:36:13,925 --> 00:36:14,926
很棒吧?
Isn't it great?

445
00:36:15,135 --> 00:36:16,845
所以 你都躲到哪去啦?
Where have you been hiding?

446
00:36:17,262 --> 00:36:18,889
我没有躲起来
I haven't been hiding.

447
00:36:18,972 --> 00:36:22,059
-我都没看到你 -你在找我?
-I haven't seen you around. -You been looking?

448
00:36:22,350 --> 00:36:24,061
-算是吧 -算是?
-Sort of. -Sort of?

449
00:36:24,603 --> 00:36:26,813
我以为你还在生我的气
I thought you were still angry with me.

450
00:36:27,522 --> 00:36:30,525
-为什么? -因为我上次见到你时说的话
-Why? -Because of what I said last time I saw you.

451
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:32,611
不 我想过很多了
I've been thinking a lot about that.

452
00:36:32,736 --> 00:36:35,322
我知道 但我该学学管自己的事就好
I should learn to mind my own business.

453
00:36:35,822 --> 00:36:39,659
不 我想你说要面对问题是对的 我也这么觉得
No, I think you're right about facing things. I feel the same way.

454
00:36:40,285 --> 00:36:42,329
我只是忘记了
I just kind of forgot for a while.

455
00:36:42,496 --> 00:36:45,499
-谢谢你提醒了我 -不客气
-Thanks for reminding me. -You're welcome.

456
00:36:47,334 --> 00:36:50,337
他认为他可以对别人为所欲为
He thinks he can do whatever he wants to people.

457
00:36:51,004 --> 00:36:52,714
-谁? -强尼
-Who? -Johnny.

458
00:36:53,090 --> 00:36:55,425
我真希望有人能对他以牙还牙
I'd love to see him get some of his own medicine.

459
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:57,594
哦 恶会有恶报的
What goes around comes around.

460
00:36:57,803 --> 00:37:00,806
-我希望到时候我可以在场 -我也是
-I'd love to be there when it does. -Me, too.

461
00:37:07,229 --> 00:37:09,106
你想不想出去?
You want to go outside?

462
00:37:11,066 --> 00:37:12,526
你说服我了
You talked me into it.

463
00:37:17,948 --> 00:37:22,327
-看看这只鸡 他疯了! -这家伙用的是真蛋
-That chicken is wild! -That guy's using real eggs!

464
00:37:22,452 --> 00:37:23,912
他真厉害
He's great!

465
00:37:24,287 --> 00:37:25,455
不!
No!

466
00:37:32,462 --> 00:37:33,672
强尼
Johnny!

467
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:39,302
强尼!
Johnny!

468
00:37:43,473 --> 00:37:45,600
-卷好麻烟没? -再等一下
-Got that number rolled? -In a minute.

469
00:37:45,684 --> 00:37:48,061
-我去叫他们 快 -好
-I'm going to get the guys. -Hurry up.

470
00:38:45,786 --> 00:38:47,037
干!
Shit!

471
00:38:47,788 --> 00:38:49,498
嘿 老兄 走开!
Move, man!

472
00:38:54,795 --> 00:38:56,671
嘿 强尼 怎么了?
Johnny, what's up?

473
00:38:58,799 --> 00:39:01,468
别挡路! 小心!
Get out of my way!

474
00:39:01,927 --> 00:39:04,346
-丹尼尔 怎么了? -报应来啦
-What's wrong? -It's coming around.

475
00:39:10,977 --> 00:39:11,937
起来!
Get up!

476
00:39:14,689 --> 00:39:15,816
别挡路!
Get out of my way!

477
00:39:23,907 --> 00:39:26,034
你他妈的在做什么?
What the hell are you doing?

478
00:39:26,827 --> 00:39:28,286
快走开!
Get out of the way!

479
00:40:03,822 --> 00:40:05,449
他过不去的
You ain't going nowhere.

480
00:40:08,305 --> 00:40:09,795
抓到他了

481
00:40:10,704 --> 00:40:12,497
你这个懦弱鬼
You little wimp!

482
00:40:15,208 --> 00:40:18,378
你就是忍不住 对吧 懦弱鬼?
You couldn't leave well enough alone, could you, little twerp?

483
00:40:18,545 --> 00:40:21,548
不 你就是要惹我们 现在该你尝苦头了
No, you had to push it. Well, now you're gonna pay!

484
00:40:24,342 --> 00:40:26,470
你要去哪里?
Where are you going, sweetheart?

485
00:40:26,762 --> 00:40:28,889
怎么啦? 想踢强尼吗?
How about a front kick, Johnny?

486
00:40:33,435 --> 00:40:34,519
拉他起来
Get him up.

487
00:40:34,644 --> 00:40:36,772
-别管他了 他也受够了 -闭嘴 巴比!
-He's had enough. -Shut up!

488
00:40:36,855 --> 00:40:40,692
-看看他 连站都站不起来了 -那又怎样? 那又不代表什么
-He can't even stand up. -That don't mean squat.

489
00:40:41,151 --> 00:40:45,197
-强尼 放了他 打够了 -我来决定打够他了没
-Johnny, he's had enough. -I'll decide when he's had enough.

490
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,157
