What's wrong with you, Johnny?

491
00:40:47,282 --> 00:40:50,368
-对敌人不可以心软 对吧? -对
-An enemy deserves no mercy. -Right!

492
00:40:50,952 --> 00:40:52,579
你疯了!
You're crazy, man!

493
00:40:57,709 --> 00:40:59,336
强尼 巴比 打他!
Get him!

