底特律
Detroit.

699
00:56:18,505 --> 00:56:19,965
磨光
Wax on...

700
00:56:20,757 --> 00:56:22,718
上蜡 右手 画圆圈
... right hand make circle.

701
00:56:22,801 --> 00:56:25,554
磨光 左手 圆圈
Wax off, left hand make circle.

702
00:56:25,887 --> 00:56:28,890
上蜡 磨光
Wax on, wax off.

703
00:56:29,182 --> 00:56:32,269
吸气 吐气
Breathe in, breathe out.

704
00:56:32,561 --> 00:56:35,564
上蜡 磨光
Wax on, wax off.

