Mr. Miyagi, I'm finished.

706
00:57:12,392 --> 00:57:14,102
你要检查吗?
You want to check these out?

707
00:57:15,479 --> 00:57:16,730
宫城先生?
Mr. Miyagi?

708
00:57:19,024 --> 00:57:20,067
宫城先生?
Mr. Miyagi?

709
00:57:27,240 --> 00:57:28,450
哈罗?
Hello?

710
00:58:05,404 --> 00:58:08,073
你在这里 我到处找你
I've been looking all over for you. Where've you been?

711
00:58:08,240 --> 00:58:10,450
-你到哪去了? -我真不敢相信
-I don't believe it. -What?

712
00:58:10,700 --> 00:58:13,954
-什么? 你要去哪? -我要去找那个混蛋 这该停止了
-Where are you going? -I'm going to find that idiot.

713
00:58:14,037 --> 00:58:16,707
-不 我会应付这一切的 -直到下一次?
-No, it's been taken care of. -Until next time.

714
00:58:16,873 --> 00:58:19,710
-不会有下次 -他们来了
-There isn't going to be a "next time." -There they are.

715
00:58:20,377 --> 00:58:23,964
