Watch this. Hey, guys, it's good to see you.

716
00:58:24,506 --> 00:58:27,175
强尼 打伤你眼睛真是抱歉 汤米 你肩膀没事吧?
Sorry about your eye, Johnny. Your shoulder okay, Tommy?

717
00:58:27,426 --> 00:58:30,345
你们最好小心 别再添更多淤青了 好吗?
You guys be careful not to step in front of any more buses.

718
00:58:31,304 --> 00:58:34,725
慢着 记得老师说的话? 你得等到比赛
Hold it. Remember what Sensei said? Wait for the tournament.

719
00:58:34,850 --> 00:58:37,227
一定是跟懦弱鬼散步周!
It must be "Take a Worm for a Walk" week.

720
00:58:39,855 --> 00:58:41,398
是你打伤他们的?
You did all that damage?

721
00:58:41,481 --> 00:58:44,234
你不知道在浴室里许的愿 都会成真吗?
When you make a wish in the shower, it always comes true.

722
00:58:44,317 --> 00:58:47,487
-我真该闭嘴的 -不 我们有协议
