-Is that your address? -You got it.

733
00:59:20,937 --> 00:59:22,397
这在哪里?
Where is this?

734
00:59:23,273 --> 00:59:25,067
-我得走了 -好
-I've got to go. -Okay.

735
00:59:25,150 --> 00:59:28,153
好 待会再跟你聊
I'll talk to you later. Great.

736
00:59:29,029 --> 00:59:30,197
太好了
All right.

737
00:59:33,784 --> 00:59:38,246
