I guess that leaves you and me, but that's all right.

743
00:59:58,392 --> 01:00:00,852
然后你再去告诉你朋友们
You can tell them about it later.

744
01:00:00,936 --> 01:00:05,148
高原印地安人是全北美洲里 非常原始的部族
The Plains Indians were a very primitive tribe...

