Come on, Casanova.

746
01:00:48,108 --> 01:00:50,485
-嗨 嗨 你好吗? -我很好
-Hi, how are you doing? -Good.

747
01:00:50,610 --> 01:00:52,904
-你真漂亮 -谢谢
-You look nice. -Thank you.

748
01:00:53,113 --> 01:00:54,823
你有客人
You've got company.

749
01:00:54,948 --> 01:00:58,368
那是我父母 来 我带你去见他们
Those are my parents. Come on, I want you to meet them.

750
01:00:58,493 --> 01:00:59,953
好
Great.

751
01:01:00,579 --> 01:01:02,372
-哈罗 甜心 -嗨 爸
-Hello, sweetheart. -Hi, Dad.

752
01:01:02,456 --> 01:01:04,833
