This is Daniel LaRusso.

753
01:01:04,958 --> 01:01:07,961
-他们是我爸妈 密尔斯先生太太 -丹尼尔 你好 嗨
-My parents, Mr. And Mrs. Mills. -How do you do, Daniel?

754
01:01:09,004 --> 01:01:11,131
-哈罗 -很高兴见到你们
-Hello, Daniel. -Nice to meet you.

755
01:01:11,256 --> 01:01:14,259
-甜心 你们要去哪? -我不知道 我们要去哪?
-Where are you going? -I don't know. Where are we going?

756
01:01:14,384 --> 01:01:16,178
我不知道 随便你想去
I don't know. Wherever you want.

757
01:01:16,261 --> 01:01:19,514
-高尔夫乐园? -好啊 我们就去高尔夫乐园
-Golf N' Stuff? -We're going to Golf N' Stuff, then.

758
01:01:20,557 --> 01:01:23,477
别担心那个 我以为你会把它修好?
Don't worry about that. Weren't you going to have that fixed?

759
01:01:23,560 --> 01:01:25,520
我是 我会的
I am. I was. I will.

760
01:01:25,645 --> 01:01:29,566
-丹尼尔 你住安西诺吗? -什么? 安西诺? 不
-You live in Encino, Daniel? -Encino? No.

761
01:01:30,192 --> 01:01:34,237
-你住哪里? -在 嗯 罗瑟达那边
-Where do you live? -Out, like Reseda.

762
01:01:35,989 --> 01:01:39,576
-那是你母亲? -对 是她
-And that's your mother? -Yeah, that's her.

763
01:01:39,701 --> 01:01:40,952
嗨!
Hi!

764
01:01:41,369 --> 01:01:44,206
她在等我们 我们快走吧 很高兴认识你们
She's waiting for us. We'd better go. Nice to meet you.

765
01:01:44,331 --> 01:01:47,000
-别太晚回家 甜心 -好 爸爸
-Not too late, sweetheart. -Okay, Dad.

766
01:01:48,056 --> 01:01:49,853
我觉得好像呆瓜

767
01:01:51,713 --> 01:01:56,259
-嗨 拉罗素太太 我叫艾莉 -嗨 艾莉 叫我露西欧
-Hi, Mrs. LaRusso. I'm Ali. -Hi, Ali. Call me Lucille.

768
01:01:57,219 --> 01:02:00,138
-好 你家真漂亮 -谢谢
-That's a beautiful house you have. -Thanks.

769
01:02:07,562 --> 01:02:09,106
-你会开手排吗? -会
-Can you drive a stick? -Yeah.

770
01:02:09,815 --> 01:02:13,693
好 打二档 让车前进 等我说"开动"时你就开动
Put it into second, let it roll, and when I say "pop it, " pop it.

771
01:02:13,860 --> 01:02:14,945
开动
"Pop it."

772
01:02:20,325 --> 01:02:22,619
别担心 情况在控制中
Don't worry, it's all under control.

773
01:02:23,370 --> 01:02:26,373
她很可爱 车子每次都这样
She's cute. It happens a lot.

774
01:02:26,748 --> 01:02:30,961
好 拉罗素! 再推! 好 哈士奇!
Okay, LaRusso, push! On, you huskies!

775
01:02:31,086 --> 01:02:33,296
好 开动!
Okay, pop it!

776
01:02:34,005 --> 01:02:36,383
成功了 拉罗素!
We got it on the first!

777
01:02:44,078 --> 01:02:46,444
高尔夫乐园 -家庭娱乐中心

778
01:02:47,682 --> 01:02:49,582
商场 -游乐 -奖品

779
01:02:54,693 --> 01:02:58,905
我11点来接你们 别玩得太晚 好好玩吧
I'll pick you up at 11:00. Please, don't be late. Have fun.

