01:46:13,875 --> 01:46:18,505
哟 各位 看看谁在这里 我们的小朋友 丹妮儿
Well, look who we have here. Our little friend Danielle.

1216
01:46:18,630 --> 01:46:20,173
哈罗 丹妮儿
Hello, Danielle.

1217
01:46:20,298 --> 01:46:23,385
怎么回事? 妈咪没帮你穿好衣服?
What's the matter? Mommy not here to dress you?

1218
01:46:24,386 --> 01:46:27,889
我在跟你说话 小子 来呀 来打呀!
I'm talking to you, punk. Come on, make a move.

1219
01:46:27,973 --> 01:46:29,850
嘿 等上场再打
Hey, save it for the ring.

1220
01:46:30,100 --> 01:46:31,101
走吧
Come on!

1221
01:46:31,810 --> 01:46:33,770
-好吧 -我们走
-All right. -Let's go.

1222
01:46:34,521 --> 01:46:35,605
走
Come on.

1223
01:46:35,772 --> 01:46:37,899
不管有无点数…
Points or no points...

1224
01:46:39,067 --> 01:46:40,318
你都死定了
... you're dead meat.

1225
01:46:41,236 --> 01:46:43,280
我叫你们出去!
I said out!

1226
01:46:45,657 --> 01:46:47,117
死定了
Dead meat.

1227
01:46:50,954 --> 01:46:53,415
少来了 我猜他会哭的
Way to go, I think he's gonna cry.

1228
01:47:03,800 --> 01:47:08,972
自由参赛第一场的胜利者是 路卡斯史奈德
The winner of the first match in the open division is Rufus Schneider.

1229
01:47:09,598 --> 01:47:13,351
-嗨 宫城先生 -丹尼尔桑 快点来 比赛要开始了
-Mr. Miyagi. -Hurry. Tournament starting.

1230
01:47:13,435 --> 01:47:14,186
这是哪来的?
Where'd we get this?

1231
01:47:14,269 --> 01:47:15,020
丹尼尔拉罗素
Daniel LaRusso...

1232
01:47:15,103 --> 01:47:18,523
-佛祖提供的 -请立刻到3号场地报到
 -Buddha provide. -... please report to Ring 3.

1233
01:47:18,774 --> 01:47:20,400
-3号场地在哪? -那里
-Where's Ring 3? -Over there.

1234
01:47:20,525 --> 01:47:24,029
等等! 只有老师和学生 才能上比赛场地 抱歉
Hold it! Sorry, teachers and students only.

1235
01:47:24,780 --> 01:47:26,323
他不会说英文
He doesn't speak English...

1236
01:47:26,448 --> 01:47:30,494
没有她的翻译我听不懂他的指示 她是他的翻译
... and I can't understand his instructions without her. She's his translator.

1237
01:47:31,828 --> 01:47:36,708
-他说什么? -你让他想起在东京的舅舅
-What did he say? -You remind him of his uncle in Tokyo.

1238
01:47:36,792 --> 01:47:41,922
-我想应该没问题 什么? -他说你很好
-I guess it's okay. What? -He says you're very kind.

1239
01:47:42,214 --> 01:47:44,091
-谢谢 -不客气
-Thank you. -Welcome.

1240
01:47:46,635 --> 01:47:49,179
-这里的规则怎样? -不知道
-What are the rules here? -I don't know.

1241
01:47:49,930 --> 01:47:51,973
你第一次 我第一次
First time you, first time me.

1242
01:47:52,099 --> 01:47:55,852
我以为你知道这些事 以前也参加过
I figured you knew about this stuff. I figured you went to these before.

1243
01:47:55,936 --> 01:47:57,145
那我死定了
Great, I'm dead.

1244
01:47:57,270 --> 01:48:01,024
-你说你打过很多次 -求生 不是求点数
-You told me you fought a lot. -For life, not for points.

1245
01:48:01,400 --> 01:48:03,610
只要击中腰部以上就得点数
Everything above your waist is a point.

1246
01:48:03,860 --> 01:48:07,280
你可以攻击头部 胸部 腰部 和肋骨 懂吗?
You can hit the head, sternum, kidneys, ribs. Got it?

1247
01:48:07,406 --> 01:48:09,616
-希望如此 -你做得到的
-I hope so. -You can do it.

1248
01:48:09,950 --> 01:48:12,327
你们这些混蛋何时才会长大?
When are you jerks going to grow up?

1249
01:48:18,750 --> 01:48:21,837
-我要去哪? 这里这个吗? -3号
-Where am I, over here at this one? -Number 3.

1250
01:48:21,920 --> 01:48:24,047
-那个人跪在那里干嘛? -不知道
-What's that guy kneeling for? -I don't know.

1251
01:48:24,172 --> 01:48:27,259
-你什么事情都不知道吗? -打 赢得点数
-Don't you know anything? -Don't get hit.

1252
01:48:36,643 --> 01:48:39,896
鞠躬 面对面
Face. Bow. On guard.

1253
01:48:41,231 --> 01:48:41,998
开始!
Fight.

1254
01:48:48,405 --> 01:48:49,656
回到线上
Back on your line.

1255
01:48:49,823 --> 01:48:51,867
-坚强点 丹尼尔 -无点数 预备
-Be tough, Daniel. -Get Ready

1256
01:48:54,369 --> 01:48:55,829
加油! 坚强点!
Come on, be tough.

1257
01:48:58,874 --> 01:49:02,711
记得你要防卫 别想点数 专心 集中力量
Remember your defence. Points coming. Concentrate. Focus power.

1258
01:49:02,794 --> 01:49:05,088
记得平衡 好好去打
Remember balance. Make good fight.

1259
01:49:07,049 --> 01:49:10,302
警告走出场外 再出场就会失分
Run out of the ring once more, it'll cost you a point.

1260
01:49:10,385 --> 01:49:12,262
预备 准备好了?
On guard. Ready?

1261
01:49:20,645 --> 01:49:22,856
好 丹尼尔 得分 加油!
That's one, Daniel, come on.

1262
01:49:25,358 --> 01:49:26,818
再来
One more!

1263
01:49:27,527 --> 01:49:29,071
回到你的线上
Move back on your line.

1264
01:49:29,988 --> 01:49:32,282
赢得一点 回旋踢
That's one point, round kick.

1265
01:49:33,575 --> 01:49:36,578
太好了 丹尼尔! 你是最棒的!
Daniel, you're the best!

1266
01:49:36,989 --> 01:49:38,149
眼镜蛇凯

1267
01:49:53,553 --> 01:49:54,888
你完蛋了 死定了!
You're dead!

1268
01:50:23,935 --> 01:50:25,425
得点 获胜

1269
01:51:36,990 --> 01:51:38,784
得点 获胜
Point! Winner!

1270
01:51:43,749 --> 01:51:47,617
拉罗素 -道区

1271
01:52:28,166 --> 01:52:29,418
获胜
Winner!

1272
01:52:32,379 --> 01:52:34,423
-要贴紧 -在这里
-It must be tight. -Yeah, right there.

1273
01:52:35,006 --> 01:52:37,926
-没想到我能撑这么久 -我也是
-I never thought I'd get this far. -Make two of us.

1274
01:52:38,009 --> 01:52:39,720
要是能赢会有多棒?
Wouldn't it be great if I won?

1275
01:52:39,886 --> 01:52:43,724
-你能活下来就很棒了 -什么意思 活下来?
-It'd be great if you survive. -What do you mean "survive"?

1276
01:52:44,224 --> 01:52:48,270
-对 只要我不动就好 -我们得走了 你得去签到 他们要开始了
-I'm fine as long as I don't move. -You've got to move now, they're starting.

1277
01:52:48,437 --> 01:52:51,606
要开始了? 什么意思 活下来?
Are they starting now? What do you mean "survive"?

1278
01:52:52,816 --> 01:52:56,153
各位先生女士…
Ladies and gentlemen...

1279
01:52:56,278 --> 01:52:59,698
请各位注意好吗?
... may I have your attention, please.

1280
01:52:59,906 --> 01:53:05,120
这是今天下午的第一场准决赛
This is the first semi -final match of the afternoon.

1281
01:53:07,456 --> 01:53:12,669
防守冠军 眼镜蛇凯的约翰劳伦斯…
Defending champion, John Lawrence of the Cobra Kai.

1282
01:53:12,961 --> 01:53:16,798
18岁以下金奖全谷区大赛的两次赢家
Two -time winner of the All Valley Under -18 Golden Trophy.

1283
01:53:16,923 --> 01:53:21,636
他将迎战罗克斯河谷空手道俱乐部的 丹尼多佛
He'll be facing Darryl Vidal of the Locust Valley Karate Club.

1284
01:53:22,345 --> 01:53:26,975
三点得胜 请双方入场好吗?
Three points wins. Contestants, please come to the ring.

1285
01:53:27,559 --> 01:53:29,519
祝两位好运
Good luck, gentlemen.

1286
01:53:31,646 --> 01:53:33,440
打他 强尼!
Go get him, Johnny.

1287
01:53:34,316 --> 01:53:35,859
嘿 小子 给他看看你的厉害!
Show him what you're made of.

1288
01:53:36,318 --> 01:53:38,278
两位面对我 鞠躬 面对面
Face me, gentlemen. Bow.

1289
01:53:38,945 --> 01:53:41,782
鞠躬 准备好了? 开始!
Face. Bow. Ready?

1290
01:53:43,575 --> 01:53:44,659
加油 强尼!
Come on, Johnny.

1291
01:53:47,496 --> 01:53:49,456
快 强尼 上 上
Fast, Johnny. Come on. Do it.

1292
01:53:54,461 --> 01:53:56,171
一点 劳伦斯
One point, Lawrence.

1293
01:54:05,847 --> 01:54:07,391
劳伦斯
Lawrence, back on the line.

1294
01:54:07,516 --> 01:54:08,809
回到线上
Way to go!

1295
01:54:08,975 --> 01:54:10,519
你还好吧?
Are you all right?

1296
01:54:10,811 --> 01:54:11,978
我没事
I'm okay.

1297
01:54:14,314 --> 01:54:15,857
一点 劳伦斯
One point, Lawrence.

1298
01:54:20,612 --> 01:54:22,572
很好 强尼
Good point, Johnny!

1299
01:54:24,491 --> 01:54:26,368
劳伦斯得点 获胜!
Point Lawrence. Winner!

1300
01:54:29,788 --> 01:54:35,001
下场准决赛将决定…谁将迎战防守冠军
The next semi -final determines who will face the defending champion.

1301
01:54:35,460 --> 01:54:41,442
宫城派空手道的…丹尼尔拉罗素能否…
Daniel LaRusso, of the Miyagi -do Karate.

1302
01:54:43,719 --> 01:54:45,095
挑战眼镜蛇凯的巴比布朗…
Bobby...

1303
01:54:45,637 --> 01:54:47,597
我要他重伤
... I want him out of commission.

1304
01:54:47,723 --> 01:54:50,183
可是老师 我打得过这小子
Sensei, I can beat this guy.

1305
01:54:52,018 --> 01:54:55,772
-我不要他被打 -可是我会失去资格!
-I don't want him beaten. -But I'll be disqualified!

1306
01:54:56,064 --> 01:54:57,858
重伤
Out of commission.

1307
01:55:01,611 --> 01:55:04,364
开始吧 两位!
Let's go, fellas. Good luck.

1308
01:55:14,124 --> 01:55:16,168
巴比 做你该做的!
Do what you got to do, Bobby!

1309
01:55:20,422 --> 01:55:24,551
鞠躬 准备好了吗?
Face. Bow. Ready?

1310
01:55:25,177 --> 01:55:27,929
两位等我指令再开始
Watch the control, gentlemen. Ready?

1311
01:55:36,438 --> 01:55:40,400
-丹尼尔 对不起! 我不是故意的! -我的腿!
-I'm sorry! I didn't mean it. -My leg!

1312
01:55:41,401 --> 01:55:45,447
-宫城先生 我的腿好痛! -丹尼尔桑 宫城在这里 没事
-Mr. Miyagi, my leg hurts. -Miyagi here.

1313
01:55:47,949 --> 01:55:52,245
眼镜蛇凯的巴比布朗 因蓄意重击对手…
Bobby Brown of the Cobra Kai has been disqualified...

1314
01:55:52,662 --> 01:55:57,376
而丧失资格 根据41-2条规定…
... for excessive and deliberate contact. Under rule 41-2...

1315
01:55:58,251 --> 01:56:02,089
丹尼尔拉罗素有15分钟回到比赛
... Daniel LaRusso has 15 minutes to return to the ring.

1316
01:56:02,172 --> 01:56:04,549
如果拉罗素无法比赛…
If he is unable to return...

1317
01:56:04,633 --> 01:56:08,929
约翰劳伦斯将获得冠军
... John Lawrence will win by default.

1318
01:56:13,850 --> 01:56:15,644
我去通知裁判
I'll inform the judges.

1319
01:56:17,020 --> 01:56:18,730
年轻人 你做得很好
You did well out there, young man.

1320
01:56:23,693 --> 01:56:24,694
该死的!
Damn it!

1321
01:56:24,861 --> 01:56:26,988
甜心 算了吧
Honey, forget it.

1322
01:56:27,155 --> 01:56:29,366
你打得很棒!
You were great.

1323
01:56:29,866 --> 01:56:31,910
我骄傲极了
I couldn't be prouder.

1324
01:56:32,411 --> 01:56:34,121
只是运气不好
It was just bad luck.

1325
01:56:34,246 --> 01:56:36,998
如果他们没有作弊 你会赢的
You would have won if they hadn't cheated.

1326
01:56:37,165 --> 01:56:39,459
让我静一静好吗?
Just leave me alone for a minute.

1327
01:56:39,584 --> 01:56:41,044
我们在外面等
We'll be outside.

1328
01:56:46,299 --> 01:56:47,926
宫城先生…
Mr. Miyagi...

1329
01:56:50,595 --> 01:56:52,806
你认为我有机会赢吗?
... you think I had a chance of winning?

1330
01:56:52,973 --> 01:56:54,516
输赢都不重要
Win, lose, no matter.

1331
01:56:54,641 --> 01:56:56,518
我不是这个意思
That's not what I mean.

1332
01:57:01,356 --> 01:57:03,316
很有机会
Had good chance.

1333
01:57:04,317 --> 01:57:07,237
你能不能像上次那样 让我的腿好起来?
Can you fix my leg with that thing you do?

1334
01:57:07,487 --> 01:57:09,781
不需要再打了
No need fight anymore.

1335
01:57:09,948 --> 01:57:13,368
-你已证明了 -什么? 证明我可以被打吗?
-You proved a point. -What, that I can take a beating?

1336
01:57:13,702 --> 01:57:17,372
只要我见到那些人 他们都会知道他们击败了我
Every time I see those guys, they'll know they got the best of me.

1337
01:57:19,166 --> 01:57:23,628
我再也不可能取得平衡 跟他们 跟艾莉…
I'll never have balance that way, not with them, not with Ali...

1338
01:57:27,299 --> 01:57:28,675
跟我自己都不会
... not with me.

1339
01:57:33,388 --> 01:57:34,389
嗯?
What?

1340
01:57:37,434 --> 01:57:38,810
闭上眼睛
Close eye.

1341
01:57:59,164 --> 01:58:04,336
好 各位先生女士…这是我们期待已久的时刻…
Ladies and gentlemen, this is the moment we've been waiting for.

1342
01:58:07,464 --> 01:58:09,841
丹尼尔拉罗素还要打?
Daniel LaRusso's going to fight?

1343
01:58:10,092 --> 01:58:12,636
丹尼尔拉罗素还要打?
Daniel LaRusso's going to fight!

1344
01:58:13,053 --> 01:58:17,099
这不正是比赛刺激的地方吗?
This is what it's all about, folks. You know it.

1345
01:58:18,100 --> 01:58:19,893
小子 腿怎么样?
How's the leg, son?

1346
01:58:22,020 --> 01:58:24,231
好! 大比赛来了!
All right. What a man!

1347
01:58:24,689 --> 01:58:26,983
最后比赛将决定…
The final match to determine...

1348
01:58:27,109 --> 01:58:30,112
谁能够获胜而得到…
... who'll emerge victor and champion...

1349
01:58:30,237 --> 01:58:34,533
全河谷区18岁以下空手道的冠军
... of the All Valley Under -18 Karate Championship.

1350
01:58:34,699 --> 01:58:37,869
丹尼尔拉罗素 宫城派空手道…
Daniel LaRusso, Miyaji -do Karate...

1351
01:58:38,578 --> 01:58:40,455
宫城派
Miyagi -do.

1352
01:58:40,580 --> 01:58:42,874
宫城派空手道…
Miyagi -do Karate.

1353
01:58:43,041 --> 01:58:46,294
迎战眼镜蛇凯的约翰劳伦斯
... versus John Lawrence of the Cobra Kai.

1354
01:58:46,378 --> 01:58:49,381
三点得胜 祝两位好运
Three points wins. Good luck, boys.

1355
01:58:50,048 --> 01:58:52,801
打吧 丹尼尔 你够强 你可以做到的!
Come on, Daniel! You've got this guy. You can do it.

1356
01:58:59,975 --> 01:59:01,768
面对我 鞠躬 面对面
Face me. Bow.

1357
01:59:01,935 --> 01:59:05,188
鞠躬 准备好了?
Face off. Bow. Ready?

1358
01:59:05,290 --> 01:59:06,723
-开始 -打倒他!
-Begin -Down down

1359
01:59:14,865 --> 01:59:16,032
没关系 强尼!
That's okay, Johnny.

1360
01:59:16,158 --> 01:59:17,784
劳伦斯 回来
Lawrence, return.

1361
01:59:19,286 --> 01:59:21,079
一点 拉罗素
One point, LaRusso.

1362
01:59:21,204 --> 01:59:22,456
你死定了
You're dead.

1363
01:59:23,107 --> 01:59:24,972
-好 丹尼尔! -开始!
-Ah Daniel! -Hey

1364
01:59:29,129 --> 01:59:30,589
你抓到他了 丹尼尔!
Daniel, you've got him!

1365
01:59:37,387 --> 01:59:40,307
斩击得点! 拉罗素得了两点!
Point! Jab! That's two for LaRusso.

1366
01:59:41,183 --> 01:59:44,186
中场休息! 去老师那边
Time out. Go to your sensei.

1367
01:59:44,352 --> 01:59:45,979
转身 跪下
Turn, kneel.

1368
01:59:46,146 --> 01:59:48,523
强尼 你是最棒的
Johnny, you're a creampuff!

1369
01:59:49,649 --> 01:59:50,817
从下面扫踢他伤处
Sweep the leg.

1370
01:59:53,403 --> 01:59:55,363
你有问题吗?
You have a problem with that?

1371
01:59:57,449 --> 01:59:58,700
可是 老师…
No, Sensei.

1372
02:00:00,786 --> 02:00:02,162
不心软
No mercy.

1373
02:00:10,962 --> 02:00:12,339
再来
One more!

1374
02:00:13,131 --> 02:00:16,134
拉罗素得两点 劳伦斯无点
Two points LaRusso. Lawrence nothing.

1375
02:00:22,567 --> 02:00:23,591
好!

1376
02:00:24,101 --> 02:00:27,771
劳伦斯得一点 二比一 拉罗素领先
One point Lawrence. 2-1, LaRusso.

1377
02:00:28,473 --> 02:00:30,100
好了? 开始!

1378
02:00:31,142 --> 02:00:32,666
来呀 打得好!

1379
02:00:48,709 --> 02:00:52,212
踢旁边 劳伦斯得一点 二比二
Kick to the side. One point Lawrence. 2-2.

1380
02:01:00,011 --> 02:01:02,222
出场 回来
Out of bounds. Come back in.

1381
02:01:04,391 --> 02:01:05,934
强尼 打败他!
Destroy him, Johnny!

1382
02:01:06,017 --> 02:01:08,311
丹尼尔 你做得到! 加油!
Come on, Daniel, you can do it!

1383
02:01:14,919 --> 02:01:16,284
好 强尼!

1384
02:01:29,750 --> 02:01:32,753
起来 坚强点!
Come on, Daniel. Be strong.

1385
02:01:35,047 --> 02:01:36,840
-你还好吗? -对 我可以
-Are you okay? -Yeah, I'm okay.

1386
